{"title":"信仰","authors":["王辽生"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":9,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"信仰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王辽生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信仰因膨胀而堕入迷醉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裂肝碎胆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸不出一声清脆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无须我左顾右盼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋已为我推开了门扉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我明知那边有冰凉的风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我还是毅然跨入"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑看日瘦月肥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至于你慨然赠我的那轮秋波"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一经收藏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反害我七情腾沸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不想进庙堂祈求超度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也淡了人间是非"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只求沿地火一意孤行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为你所设计的拔萃工程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作最后的鼓吹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉我吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我与生俱来的中华之恋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可感知正有人憔悴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意志鲜红而无声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夕阳悬垂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱是一种不老的轮回"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}